@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bauheo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = 0.27
    v2 = (v2 - wp.exp((v0 + 0.60 / v1 + 0.03)))
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.57 - tmp + 0.56) + (v2 + 0.09 * v1 + 0.79)) + wp.sin((v2 + 0.52 * v2 + 0.01)))
    v1 = (0.33 - v0)
    tmp = wp.cos((tmp - wp.cos(v1 + 0.62)))
    data[tid] = v0
